    "id": "NWNFWGQNVP2XXLMLFUOC7P3F",
    "name": "Bronze Boost Tanning Water 2oz",
    "price": "$15.00",
    "descriptionText": "These products are available for purchase during your spray tan appointment at Coastal Bronze. Shipping and online checkout are not currently available.\n- Refresh color between spray tans\n- Adds a subtle boost of color without streaking\n- Clear formula with zero risk of transfer to clothes or sheets\n- Perfect for maintaining your glow between appointments\n\nDirections: Apply 4-8 sprays from an arms-length distance onto desired areas. Use sparingly on knees, elbows, and ankles. Rinse in 8-12 hours with lukewarm water only - No soaps or scrubs. Moisturize daily to maintain skin hydration for long-lasting color.\nKey Ingredients: Vitamin C | Cucumber Extract | Aloe Vera | Bamboo Extract | Jojoba Seed Oil | White Tea Extract",
