    "name": "Bronze Glow Tan Extender 2oz",
    "price": "$10.00",
    "descriptionText": "These products are available for purchase during your spray tan appointment at Coastal Bronze. Shipping and online checkout are not currently available.\n- Extend your tan up to several extra days\n- Hydrates skin for more even fading\n- Gradually maintains color for a longer-lasting tan\n- Helps your spray tan fade evenly instead of patchy\n\nDirections: Apply once per day, every other day, starting after day three of spray tan application to extend the life of your spray tan. Wash hands immediately after application to prevent staining.\nKey Ingredients: Soybean Oil | Hyaluronic Acid | Kakadu Plum Fruit Extract | Vitamin C | Aloe | Jojoba Seed Oil | Cucumber Fruit Extract",
